         RootTransparent buffer, Tint #edeceb 50, IconAlpha 60
Colorset 2 fg white, bg #1883f1, sh black, hi black, fgsh black, \
         RootTransparent buffer, Tint #edeceb 50, IconAlpha 95

# 窗口色彩 Decoration Colorsets 
